title: TNF Recap & Week 3 Locks
itunes:title: TNF Recap & Week 3 Locks
description:
In a room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling & a phone calling Marc Sessler – react to the Browns shattering their 635-day winless streak (:30) and share their ‘Week 3 Locks’, including the Saints and Falcons NFC South clash (21:30), the “Desperation Bowl” in Houston (36:20), Jimmy Garoppolo and the 49ers cross Patrick Mahomes in KC (45:10), is Aaron Rodgers still OK to play against Washington (1:00:10), will Josh Rosen play against Chicago’s stifling defense (1:07:40) & Monday night is FITZMagic night (1:17:45)!
